      <title>马士基认为红海目前对其船舶来说太不安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/maersk-decides-the-red-sea-is-too-unsafe-for-its-ships-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集装箱运输巨头 A.P. 穆勒-马士基公司表示，在其另一艘承运人在几周内遭受攻击后，该公司将再次停止让其船只穿越重要的贸易走廊红海。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/maersk-decides-the-red-sea-is-too-unsafe-for-its-ships-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:38:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗的红海权力游戏引发了对贸易中断的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/iran-s-red-sea-power-play-heightens-fears-of-trade-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向红海派遣一艘军舰是迄今为止在关键贸易路线上挑战美军的最大胆举动，这让胡塞武装分子更加胆大妄为，他们的导弹在过去两个月扰乱了航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/iran-s-red-sea-power-play-heightens-fears-of-trade-disruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
